{"segment_id": "shangshu-004-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-great-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-004", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-004-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-great-yu", "source_id": "shangshu-004-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-great-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "尚書·虞書 大禹謨 [4]", "text_original": "益曰：「都，帝德廣運，乃聖乃神，乃武乃文。皇天眷命，奄有四海為天下君。」", "text_normalized": "益曰：「都，帝德廣運，乃聖乃神，乃武乃文。皇天眷命，奄有四海為天下君。」", "notes": ""}
