{"segment_id": "shangshu-004-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-great-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-007", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-004-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-great-yu", "source_id": "shangshu-004-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-great-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 7, "canonical_ref": "尚書·虞書 大禹謨 [7]", "text_original": "禹曰：「於！帝念哉！德惟善政，政在養民。水、火、金、木、土、穀，惟修；正德、利用、厚生、惟和。九功惟敘，九敘惟歌。戒之用休，董之用威，勸之以九歌俾勿壞。」", "text_normalized": "禹曰：「於！帝念哉！德惟善政，政在養民。水、火、金、木、土、穀，惟修；正德、利用、厚生、惟和。九功惟敘，九敘惟歌。戒之用休，董之用威，勸之以九歌俾勿壞。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-004-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-great-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-008", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-004-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-great-yu", "source_id": "shangshu-004-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-great-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 8, "canonical_ref": "尚書·虞書 大禹謨 [8]", "text_original": "帝曰：「俞！地平天成，六府三事允治，萬世永賴，時乃功。」", "text_normalized": "帝曰：「俞！地平天成，六府三事允治，萬世永賴，時乃功。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-004-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-great-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-009", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-004-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-great-yu", "source_id": "shangshu-004-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-great-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 9, "canonical_ref": "尚書·虞書 大禹謨 [9]", "text_original": "帝曰：「格，汝禹！朕宅帝位三十有三載，耄期倦于勤。汝惟不怠，總朕師。」", "text_normalized": "帝曰：「格，汝禹！朕宅帝位三十有三載，耄期倦于勤。汝惟不怠，總朕師。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-004-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-great-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-010", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-004-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-great-yu", "source_id": "shangshu-004-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-great-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 10, "canonical_ref": "尚書·虞書 大禹謨 [10]", "text_original": "禹曰：「朕德罔克，民不依。皋陶邁種德，德乃降，黎民懷之。帝念哉！念茲在茲，釋茲在茲，名言茲在茲，允出茲在茲，惟帝念功。」", "text_normalized": "禹曰：「朕德罔克，民不依。皋陶邁種德，德乃降，黎民懷之。帝念哉！念茲在茲，釋茲在茲，名言茲在茲，允出茲在茲，惟帝念功。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-004-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-great-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-011", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-004-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-great-yu", "source_id": "shangshu-004-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-great-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 11, "canonical_ref": "尚書·虞書 大禹謨 [11]", "text_original": "帝曰：「皋陶，惟茲臣庶，罔或干予正。汝作士，明于五刑，以弼五教。期于予治，刑期于無刑，民協于中，時乃功，懋哉。」", "text_normalized": "帝曰：「皋陶，惟茲臣庶，罔或干予正。汝作士，明于五刑，以弼五教。期于予治，刑期于無刑，民協于中，時乃功，懋哉。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-004-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-great-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-012", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-004-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-great-yu", "source_id": "shangshu-004-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-great-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 12, "canonical_ref": "尚書·虞書 大禹謨 [12]", "text_original": "皋陶曰：「帝德罔愆，臨下以簡，御眾以寬；罰弗及嗣，賞延于世。宥過無大，刑故無小；罪疑惟輕，功疑惟重；與其殺不辜，寧失不經；好生之德，洽于民心，茲用不犯于有司。」", "text_normalized": "皋陶曰：「帝德罔愆，臨下以簡，御眾以寬；罰弗及嗣，賞延于世。宥過無大，刑故無小；罪疑惟輕，功疑惟重；與其殺不辜，寧失不經；好生之德，洽于民心，茲用不犯于有司。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-004-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-great-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-013", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-004-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-great-yu", "source_id": "shangshu-004-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-great-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 13, "canonical_ref": "尚書·虞書 大禹謨 [13]", "text_original": "帝曰：「俾予從欲以治，四方風動，惟乃之休。」", "text_normalized": "帝曰：「俾予從欲以治，四方風動，惟乃之休。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-004-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-great-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-014", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-004-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-great-yu", "source_id": "shangshu-004-yu-shu-counsels-of-the-great-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 14, "canonical_ref": "尚書·虞書 大禹謨 [14]", "text_original": "帝曰：「來，禹！降水儆予，成允成功，惟汝賢。克勤于邦，克儉于家，不自滿假，惟汝賢。汝惟不矜，天下莫與汝爭能。汝惟不伐，天下莫與汝爭功。予懋乃德，嘉乃丕績，天之歷數在汝躬，汝終陟元后。人心惟危，道心惟微，惟精惟一，允執厥中。無稽之言勿聽，弗詢之謀勿庸。可愛非君？可畏非民？眾非元后，何戴？后非眾，罔與守邦？欽哉！慎乃有位，敬修其可願，四海困窮，天祿永終。惟口出好興戎，朕言不再。」", "text_normalized": "帝曰：「來，禹！降水儆予，成允成功，惟汝賢。克勤于邦，克儉于家，不自滿假，惟汝賢。汝惟不矜，天下莫與汝爭能。汝惟不伐，天下莫與汝爭功。予懋乃德，嘉乃丕績，天之歷數在汝躬，汝終陟元后。人心惟危，道心惟微，惟精惟一，允執厥中。無稽之言勿聽，弗詢之謀勿庸。可愛非君？可畏非民？眾非元后，何戴？后非眾，罔與守邦？欽哉！慎乃有位，敬修其可願，四海困窮，天祿永終。惟口出好興戎，朕言不再。」", "notes": ""}
